{"tid":2446952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普私下評哈利夫婦專訪　「梅根不是好人 」","createTime":"2021-03-15T00:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T01:51:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f390979316e5abece4fe8df13e3445e900e7dff7","tid":2446952,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:16:08.000Z","msg":"英國哈利王子和妻子梅根接受美國名主持人歐普拉專訪，引發熱烈討論。曾被梅根批評的美國前總統川普，據說看了專訪後私下認為梅根「不是好人」。<br />\n<br />\n川普前顧問米勒（Jason Miller）在川普前策士班農（Steve Bannon）Podcast節目「War Room」，透露川普對哈利梅根專訪的想法。米勒說川普告訴他：「她不是好人&hellip;&hellip;我以前說過，現在大家看見了。」<br />\n米勒說，川普曾想過公開評論專訪，但最終打消念頭，怕會有英國名嘴摩根（Piers Morgan）的下場，因說錯話而告別公眾視野。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210315/O777CG5KQJDJ5D5JG7Z6ULHPLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FO777CG5KQJDJ5D5JG7Z6ULHPLI%2F&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfEkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=7eb86bb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FO777CG5KQJDJ5D5JG7Z6ULHPLI%2F&h=0d342493\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210315/O777CG5KQJDJ5D5JG7Z6ULHPLI/</a>"},{"pid":"4ac4cccd3fa03586ac5d4a5118034aac36d78471","tid":2446952,"uid":329977,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mzh7b8S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzh7b8S.gif&h=fed9ae53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5985c487362520f364eaad8ee5ffcd6908156c54","tid":2446952,"uid":297997,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:21:48.000Z","msg":"原本條臭閪可能只係八婆一個，而家可能比惡勢力拎嚟做棋"},{"pid":"73fb49b8f914f702ff80c1298c8fb0f9acd17ef3","tid":2446952,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:24:59.000Z","msg":"大侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/